{"first_name":"Andris K.","last_name":"Berzins","permalink":"andris-berzins","crunchbase_url":"http://www.crunchbase.com/person/andris-berzins","homepage_url":"http://www.techhub.com/riga","birthplace":"Sydney, Australia","twitter_username":"akberzins","blog_url":"https://twitter.com/akberzins","blog_feed_url":"","affiliation_name":"AeroScout","born_year":1971,"born_month":9,"born_day":20,"tag_list":"startup, entrepreneur, latvia, baltic-states, restaurants, cafes, bars, pubs, loyalty, mobile, marketing, business-development","alias_list":null,"created_at":"Wed Aug 11 07:08:54 UTC 2010","updated_at":"Sun Sep 16 02:24:13 UTC 2012","overview":"<p>I am a global technology entrepreneur with a passion for building startups into successful companies.</p>\n\n<p>As angel investor and mentor, I actively support the growing Baltic rim startup community. My particular focus is helping startups from my home base of Latvia reach European, American and ultimately global markets. As such, I am co-founder and Chairman of TechHub Riga, the first expansion location for TechHub from London.</p>\n\n<p>I am a board member and advisor for a variety of startups, including Reach.ly, where I am Chairman and Co-Founder, also Infogr.am and Cobook, among others.</p>\n\n<p>Previously I have served in C-level positions, most recently at Livebookings, Europe&#8217;s leading provider of online marketing and reservations services to restaurants. Prior to that, I led business development and ran EMEA for AeroScout, a global provider of WiFi location solutions. I also worked at strategy consultcy Bain &amp; Company in Boston and Stockholm.</p>","image":{"available_sizes":[[[150,150],"assets/images/resized/0009/7653/97653v7-max-150x150.jpg"],[[250,250],"assets/images/resized/0009/7653/97653v7-max-250x250.jpg"],[[450,450],"assets/images/resized/0009/7653/97653v7-max-450x450.jpg"]],"attribution":"<p>Thanks to HackFwd for this photo</p>"},"degrees":[{"degree_type":"MBA","subject":"Business","institution"